English: A Booster Progress value exceeding {0} will be rewarded with a random Booster from the corresponding category.
Description: A text string that appears in the result screen (when you have failed or succeeded at an expedition.) This text explains the rules regarding how players are rewarded with boosters. The "corresponding category" bit refers to the fact that "muted" artifacts are rewarded with "muted" boosters, "bold" artifacts are rewarded with "bold" boosters and "aggressive" artifacts are rewarded with "aggressive" boosters.

Russian.Translation: За прогресс с усилителями {0} вы получите случайный усилитель из соответствующей категории.

Portuguese_Brazil.Translation: Um valor de progresso do impulso excedendo {0} será recompensado com um impulso aleatório da categoria correspondente.

Polish.Translation: Współczynnik postępów wzmacniaczy powyżej {0} zostanie nagrodzony losowym wzmacniaczem odpowiedniej kategorii.
